137  {
138  double lconv_perp = lconv * std::sin(conv_obliq),
139  lconv_par = lconv * std::cos(conv_obliq),
140  repeated = (std::pow(__orbital_angmom, 2)
141  +
142  std::pow(lconv, 2)

151  repeated
152  -

155  +

157  )
158  /
159  repeated
160  );
161  }
